judgment_text:
IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY

O. O. C. J.
Suit No.911 of 1987
Dena Bank 
..
.. Plaintiff 
 v/s.
Peter Francis Gonsalves & ors.
.. Defendants
Mr.Hatim i/by Nandlal Kothari& Sabir for Plaintiff.
Mr.Farukh Shaikh, S.O. in Court Receiver's office   present.
Mr.J.N . Panchal, Clerk, present of Court Receiver. 
------

CORAM : SMT.ROSHAN DALVI, J.
Dated : 23 rd January 2009
P.C. :
. The Plaintiff has got the Receiver appointed in this Suit
under the order dated 8.4.1988. The Defendants have since
made payment to the Plaintiff. The Receiver, therefore,
stands discharged subject to the payment of costs, charges
and expenses.
. The Receiver shall return all the documents of the Plaintiff.
. The Plaintiff shall be entitled to get the relevant mutation
entry entered in the Revenue Records. 
. Receiver to act certified copy of this order.

(SMT.ROSHAN DALVI, J.)
